A closer look at the AMOLED display of the Samsung Galaxy S6 with an X-Rite i1Pro 2 Spectrophotometer and the CalMAN software shows that the objective picture quality of the smartphone is very good as well. The standard display mode &ldquo;Simple&rdquo; has particularly good values that are very close to the ideal values for the colors (DeltaE of 2.51) as well as the grayscale (DeltaE of 2.59). The same applies to the color temperature, which just barely deviates from the ideal value with 6424 K.&nbsp;

